</div></td><td class="navbox-list" style="border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;padding:0px;text-align:center; padding:3px;;;background:#F5CEC3;;width:10em;"><div>
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Yevamot" title="Yevamot">Yevamot</a></li>
