<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;background:#345d9d;padding-bottom:0.15em;color:white;">Related topics</div><div class="NavContent" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center">
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Religious_abuse" title="Religious abuse">Abuse</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Apostasy" title="Apostasy">Apostasy</a>
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Apostasy_in_Islam" title="Apostasy in Islam">In Islam</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Apostasy_in_Christianity" title="Apostasy in Christianity">In Christianity</a></li></ul></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Criticism_of_atheism" title="Criticism of atheism">Criticism of atheism</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Criticism_of_monotheism" title="Criticism of monotheism">Criticism of monotheism</a></li>
