udes to Israel</i>, Yehoshafat Harkabi, pp. 248, 272</span></li><li about="#cite_note-83" id="cite_note-83"><a href="./Talmud#cite_ref-83" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-83" class="mw-reference-text">Such as <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Uriel_da_Costa" title="Uriel da Costa" id="mwBMM">Uriel da Costa</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Israel_Shahak" title="Israel Shahak" id="mwBMQ">Israel Shahak</a>, and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Baruch_Kimmerling" title="Baruch Kimmerling" id="mwBMU">Baruch Kimmerling</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-84" id="cite_note-84"><a href="./Talmud#cite_ref-84" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-84" class="mw-reference-text">Such as <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Christopher_Hitchens" title="Christopher Hitchens" id="mwBMY">Christopher Hitchens</a> and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Denis_Diderot" title="Denis Diderot" id="mwBMc">Denis Diderot</a></span></li><li about="#cite_note-85" id="cite_note-85"><a href="./Talmud#cite_ref-85" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-85" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Hyam_Maccoby" title="Hyam Maccoby" id="mwBMg">Hyam Maccoby</a>, <i id="mwBMk">Judaism on Trial</i></span></li><li about="#cite_note-86" id="cite_note-86"><a href="./Talmud#cite_ref-86" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-86" class="mw-reference-text">ADL report <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.adl.org/presrele/asus_12/the_talmud.pdf" id="mwBMo">The Talmud in Anti-Semitic Polemics</a> <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100805220714/http://www.adl.org/presrele/asus_12/the_talmud.pdf" about="#mwt272" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"weba