hon-mamre.org/e/e0000.htm English translation])\n* Maimonides &apos;&apos;Introduction to the [[Maimonides#Works and bibliography|Commentary on the Mishnah]]&apos;&apos; ([http://www.daat.ac.il/daat/mahshevt/hakdama/tohen-m-2.htm Hebrew Fulltext]),  transl. Zvi Lampel (Judaica Press, 1998). ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"1-880582-28-7"}},"i":14}},"\n* [[Aaron Parry]] &apos;&apos;The Complete Idiot&apos;s Guide to The Talmud&apos;&apos; (Alpha Books, 2004). ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"ISBN","href":"./Template:ISBN"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"1-59257-202-2"}},"i":15}},"\n* [[Michael Levi Rodkinson|Rodkinson, Michael Levi]], &apos;&apos;The history of the Talmud from the time of its formation, about 200 B.C., up to the present time&apos;&apos;, The Talmud Society, 1918\n* ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"author":{"wt":"Jonathan Rosen"},"title":{"wt":"The Talmud and the Internet: A Journey Between Worlds"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=GaAyUAKmm00C"},"accessdate":{"wt":"29 August 2011"},"date":{"wt":"2001"},"publisher":{"wt":"Continuum International Publishing Group"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-8264-5534-5"}},"i":16}},"\n* ",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"author":{"wt":"Adin Steinsaltz"},"authorlink":{"wt":"Adin Steinsaltz"},"title":{"wt":"The essential Talmud"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=keXGJjd4ThcC&amp;pg=PA10"},"accessdate":{"wt":"29 August 2011"},"date":{"wt":"2006"},"publisher":{"wt":"Basic Books"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-465-08273-5"}},"i":17}}," Read more [http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20060829004122/http://www.steinsaltz.org/dynamic/book_details.asp?id%3D22 here]. See also [https://web.archive.org/web/20060525191901/http://www.steinsaltz.org/dynamic/essay_details.asp?id=6&amp;sub=1 here].\n* [[Adin Steinsaltz]] &apos;&apos;The Talmud: A Reference Guide&apos;&apos; (Random House, 1996).