<section data-mw-section-id="51" id="mwBUI"><h4 id="Logic_and_methodology">Logic and methodology</h4>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r853264625" about="#mwt605" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw="{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;refbegin&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Refbegin&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{},&quot;i&quot;:0}},&quot;\n* [[Samuel ibn Naghrela|Samuel ha-Nagid]], ''Mevo ha-Talmud''\n* [[Joseph ben Judah ibn Aknin]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/33105 Mevo ha-Talmud]''\n* [[Zerachiah ha-Levi of Girona|Zerachiah Halevi]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/24968 Sefer ha-Tzava]''\n* [[Samson of Chinon]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/32813 Sefer ha-Keritut]''\n* [[Jacob Hagiz]], ''Teḥillat Ḥochmah'' (included in most editions of ''Keritut'')\n* collective, ed. [[Abraham ibn Akra]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/7049 Meharere Nemarim]''\n* [[Joseph ibn Verga]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/11888 She'erit Yosef]''\n* [[Isaac Campanton]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/21689 Darche ha-Talmud]''\n* [[David ben Solomon ibn Abi Zimra]], ''Kelale ha-Gemara''\n* [[Bezalel Ashkenazi]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/38786 Kelale ha-Gemara]''\n* Yeshu’ah b. Yosef ha-Levi, ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/11511 Halichot Olam]''\n** [[Joseph Caro]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/24850 Kelale ha-Gemara]'' (commentary on ''Halichot Olam'')\n** Solomon Algazi, ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/24722 Yavin Shemu’ah]'' (commentary on ''Halichot Olam'')\n* Yisrael Ya'akov Algazi, ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/31452 Ar'a de-Rabbanan]''\n* Serillo, Samuel, ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/20305 Kelale Shemuel]''\n* [[Isaiah Horowitz|Horowitz, Isaiah]], ''Shene Luchot ha-Berit'' (section on ''Torah she-be-al-Pe'')\n* [[Moses Chaim Luzzatto]], ''[http://hebrewbooks.org/19760 Derech Tevunot]'', translated into English as ''The Ways of Reason'', Feldheim 1988, &quot;,{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;ISBN&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:ISBN&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;: