<p id="mwBVk"><b id="mwBVo">Refutation of allegations concerning the Talmud</b></p>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r853264625" about="#mwt646" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"refbegin","href":"./Template:Refbegin"},"params":{},"i":0}},"\n* [http://www.angelfire.com/mt/talmud/ Talmud: The Real Truth About The Talmud], by [[Gil Student]], also available [http://talmud.faithweb.com/ here]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100805220714/http://www.adl.org/presrele/asus_12/the_talmud.pdf The Talmud in Anti-Semitic Polemics], [[Anti-Defamation League]]\n* [http://freemasonry.bcy.ca/anti-masonry/van_hyning.html Falsifiers of the Talmud]\n",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"refend","href":"./Template:Refend"},"params":{},"i":1}}]}' id="mwBVs"/><div class="refbegin   " style="" about="#mwt646" id="mwBVw">
<ul><li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.angelfire.com/mt/talmud/">Talmud: The Real Truth About The Talmud</a>, by <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Gil_Student" title="Gil Student">Gil Student</a>, also available <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://talmud.faithweb.com/">here</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100805220714/http://www.adl.org/presrele/asus_12/the_talmud.pdf">The Talmud in Anti-Semitic Polemics</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Anti-Defamation_League" title="Anti-Defamation League">Anti-Defamation League</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://freemasonry.bcy.ca/anti-masonry/van_hyning.html">Falsifiers of the Talmud</a></li></ul>
</div>

<p id="mwBV0"><b id="mwBV4">Full text resources</b></p>
<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r853264625" about="#mwt739" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"refbegin","href":"./Template:Refbegin"},"params":{},"i":0}},"\n* [https://www.sefaria.org/texts/Talmud Talmud and English translation, from the Steinsaltz edition]\n* [http://www.halakhah.com Talmud Bavli (Soncino translation)] (English). The Soncino Press translation of the Talmud Bavli in downloadable [[Portable Document Format|PDF]] format. Everything is present except for the index volume and the [http://www.worldcat.org/title/minor-tractates-of-the-talmud-massektoth-ketannoth/oclc/5423306 minor-tractates volumes].[http://tzvee.blogspot.ca/2009/04/soncino-talmud-translation-online-at.html#c9103600910012975126 About 63% of the translation is also available in the form of ordinary] [[Hypertext Markup Language|HTML]] [http://tzvee.blogspot.com/2009/04/soncino-talmud-translation-online-at.html  webpages for those who prefer them.]\n* [http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/h/h0.htm Mishnah] (Hebrew)\n* [http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/f/f0.htm Tosefta] (Hebrew)\n* [http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/r/r0.htm Talmud Yerushalmi] (Hebrew)\n* [http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/l/l0.htm Talmud Bavli] (Hebrew)\n* [http://kodesh.snunit.k12.il/ Full searchable Talmud on Snunit] (Hebrew)\n* [http://www.sacred-texts.com/jud/talmud.htm Rodkinson English translation] See above, under [[#Talmud Bavli]].\n* [http://www.e-daf.com E-Daf] Images of each page of the Babylonian Talmud\n* [http://www.nosachteiman.co.il/?CategoryID=1160&amp;ArticleID=5713&amp;SearchParam=%D7%AA%D7%9C%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%93 Tractate Megillah]: .pdf download showing Yemenite vocalization\n* [http://www.shas.org/dafviewer Shas.org Daf Viewer] (Hebrew)\n",{"template":{"target":{"wt":"refend","href":"./Template:Refend"},"params":{},"i":1}}]}' id="mwBV8"/><div class="refbegin   " style="" about="#mwt739" id="mwBWA">
<ul><li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.sefaria.org/texts/Talmud">Talmud and English translation, from the Steinsaltz edition</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.halakhah.com">Talmud Bavli (Soncino translation)</a> (English). The Soncino Press translation of the Talmud Bavli in downloadable <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Portable_Document_Format" title="Portable Document Format" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a> format. Everything is present except for the index volume and the <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/title/minor-tractates-of-the-talmud-massektoth-ketannoth/oclc/5423306">minor-tractates volumes</a>.<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://tzvee.blogspot.ca/2009/04/soncino-talmud-translation-online-at.html#c9103600910012975126">About 63% of the translation is also available in the form of ordinary</a> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Hypertext_Markup_Language" title="Hypertext Markup Language" class="mw-redirect">HTML</a> <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://tzvee.blogspot.com/2009/04/soncino-talmud-translation-online-at.html">webpages for those who prefer them.</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/h/h0.htm">Mishnah</a> (Hebrew)</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/f/f0.htm">Tosefta</a> (Hebrew)</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/r/r0.htm">Talmud Yerushalmi</a> (Hebrew)</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/b/l/l0.htm">Talmud Bavli</a> (Hebrew)</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://kodesh.snunit.k12.il/">Full searchable Talmud on Snunit</a> (Hebrew)</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.sacred-texts.com/jud/talmud.htm">Rodkinson English translation</a> See above, under <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Talmud#Talmud_Bavli">#Talmud Bavli</a>.</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.e-daf.com">E-Daf</a> Images of each page of the Babylonian Talmud</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.nosachteiman.co.il/?CategoryID=1160&amp;ArticleID=5713&amp;SearchParam=%D7%AA%D7%9C%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%93">Tractate Megillah</a>: .pdf download showing Yemenite vocalization</li>
<li><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.shas.org/dafviewer">Shas.org Daf Viewer</a> (Hebrew)</li></ul>
